  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your attention and observation in this addictive object search game. Explore the underground bunker created by the cats in anticipation of the atomic explosion and find cleverly hidden items. Background music will give you a fully immersive experience. Suitable for the whole family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 150 hidden items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- There is a hint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The map is colorable</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2.5D effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Customize brightness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Saving progress</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Scaling</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Relaxing music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- UFO</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your attention and observation in this addictive object search game. Explore the underground bunker created by the cats in anticipation of the atomic explosion and find cleverly hidden items. Background music will give you a fully immersive experience. Suitable for the whole family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 150 hidden items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- There is a hint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The map is colorable</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2.5D effect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Customize brightness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Saving progress</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Scaling</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Relaxing music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- UFO</p>",
